-sound%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConnectivity%20and%20format%20support%20are%20worth%20paying%20attention%20to%2C%20too.%20Support%20for%20Dolby%20Atmos%20rivals%20like%20DTS%3AX%20is%20a%20nice%20bonus%2C%20as%20are%20features%20like%20WiFi%20for%20high-quality%20music%20streaming.%20Extras%20such%20as%20Spotify%20Connect%2C%20Apple%20AirPlay%202%2C%20and%20a%20companion%20mobile%20app%20make%20day-to-day%20use%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20minimum%2C%20a%20Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbar%20should%20include%20an%20HDMI%20ARC%20or%20eARC%20connection%2C%20with%20eARC%20offering%20better%20bandwidth%20on%20compatible%20displays%20(which%20include%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20TVs%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Extra%20HDMI%20pass-through%20ports%20are%20helpful%20if%20you%20have%20multiple%20devices%2C%20and%20gamers%20may%20want%20HDMI%202.1%20support%20for%20features%20like%20VRR%20and%20ALLM.%20Check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-hdmi-cable%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20HDMI%20cables%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20top%20recommendations%20you%20can%20use%20with%20your%20soundbar%20and%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESize%20also%20matters.%20Make%20sure%20the%20bar%20fits%20your%20media%20console%20without%20blocking%20the%20bottom%20of%20your%20TV%2C%20especially%20if%20it's%20a%20taller%20model.%20If%20space%20is%20tight%2C%20mounting%20your%20TV%20can%20help.%20And%20if%20smart%20home%20features%20matter%20to%20you%2C%20look%20for%20a%20soundbar%20with%20built-in%20support%20for%20Amazon%20Alexa%20or%20Google%20Assistant%20via%20onboard%20microphones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ecc57f39-c619-4b37-b3e6-f013264e7f5d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDolby%20Atmos%20soundbar%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221432%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbar%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675c49bdcf8d1359a2dfcb93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221074%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAngled%20audio%20drivers%20enable%20Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbars%20to%20direct%20sound%20effects%20toward%20your%20ceiling%20and%20then%20back%20down%20to%20your%20ears.%3Cp%3EDolby%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20Dolby%20Atmos%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20is%20a%203D%20audio%20format%20designed%20to%20make%20sound%20feel%20more%20lifelike%20and%20immersive.%20It%20does%20this%20using%20object-based%20audio%20mixing.%20Rather%20than%20just%20locking%20sounds%20to%20specific%20speakers%2C%20mixers%20can%20place%20effects%20like%20buzzing%20insects%20or%20flying%20jets%20anywhere%20in%20a%20three-dimensional%20space%2C%20creating%20smoother%2C%20more%20natural%20movement%20than%20traditional%20surround%20sound.%20It%20also%20allows%20for%20the%20addition%20of%20overhead%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Dolby%20Atmos%20audio%20system%20then%20processes%20this%20mixing%20data%20and%20seamlessly%20places%20sounds%20wherever%20they're%20supposed%20to%20go%2C%20based%20on%20the%20system's%20specific%20capabilities.%20This%20means%20Dolby%20Atmos%20audio%20can%20scale%20to%20match%20a%20variety%20of%20speaker%20and%20soundbar%20setups.%20You'll%20usually%20see%20Dolby%20Atmos%20systems%20labeled%20with%20three%20numbers%2C%20such%20as%205.1.2%20or%205.1.4.%20The%20first%20two%20numbers%20refer%20to%20standard%20surround%20channels%20and%20the%20subwoofer%2C%20while%20the%20final%20number%20shows%20how%20many%20dedicated%20height%20channels%20are%20used.%20So%2C%20in%20a%205.1.2%20setup%2C%20%26quot%3B.2%26quot%3B%20means%20two%20height%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20is%20most%20impressive%20in%20movie%20theaters%2C%20where%20speakers%20can%20be%20installed%20all%20around%20and%20above%20the%20audience.%20At%20home%2C%20Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbars%20recreate%20this%20effect%20using%20up-firing%20speakers%20or%20virtual%20height%20channels%20to%20simulate%20overhead%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20information%20about%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20check%20out%20our%20complete%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-dolby-atmos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Dolby%20Atmos%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20up-firing%20speaker%20drivers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20Dolby%20Atmos%20soundbars%20use%20up-firing%20speaker%20drivers%20to%20create%20a%20sense%20of%20overhead%20audio.%20Traditional%20speaker%20drivers%20are%20positioned%20to%20beam%20sound%20forward%20or%20to%20the%20side%20at%20ear%20level.%20However%2C%20up-firing%20speaker%20drivers%20are%20angled%20upward.%20This%20allows%20them%20to%20bounce%20sound%20effects%20off%20your%20ceiling%20and%20then%20back%20down%20to%20your%20ears%2C%20simulating%20the%20effect%20of%20audio%20coming%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20less%20effective%20than%20ceiling-mounted%20speakers%2C%20up-firing%20drivers%20still%20work%20well%20when%20properly%20utilized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhere%20can%20I%20find%20Dolby%20Atmos%20movies%20and%20shows%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20are%20available%20through%20various%20sources.%20Many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fbest-streaming-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fdisney-plus%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisney%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fparamount-plus-streaming-service%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParamount%20Plus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offer%20titles%20with%20Dolby%20Atmos%20mixes.%20Dolby%20Atmos%20is%20also%20a%20popular%20format%20on%20Blu-ray%20and%204K%20Blu-ray%20releases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20there%20Dolby%20Atmos%20music%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%2C%20Dolby%20Atmos%20audio%20mixing%20is%20used%20for%20some%20music.%20This%20enables%20artists%20to%20spread%20vocals%20and%20instruments%20across%20a%203D%20space%20to%20create%20a%20surround-sound%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDolby%20Atmos%20audio%20tracks%20are%20available%20through%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-music-streaming-service-subscription%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20music%20streaming%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Amazon%20Music%20Unlimited%2C%20Apple%20Music%2C%20and%20Tidal.%20Only%20select%20albums%20are%20mixed%20in%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20but%20each%20service%20has%20a%20growing%20selection%20of%20new%20and%20classic%20tracks%20that%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20I%20play%20video%20games%20in%20Dolby%20Atmos%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20many%20modern%20video%20games%20can%20be%20played%20in%20Dolby%20Atmos.%20The%20PS5%2C%20Xbox%20Series%20X%2C%20Xbox%20Series%20S%2C%20Xbox%20One%20X%2C%20Xbox%20One%20S%2C%20and%20Windows%2010%2F11%20PCs%20all%20support%20Dolby%20Atmos%20through%20compatible%20soundbars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20DTS%3AX%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDTS%3AX%20is%20a%20rival%20audio%20format%20that%20uses%20techniques%20similar%20to%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20such%20as%20object-based%20sound%20with%20height%20elements%20for%20three-dimensional%20immersion.%20Unlike%20Dolby%20Atmos%2C%20titles%20encoded%20with%20DTS%3AX%20audio%20are%20largely%20confined%20to%20Blu-ray%20discs%2C%20and%20the%20format%20isn't%20supported%20by%20many%20streaming%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20May%202024%2C%20Disney%20Plus%20launched%20DTS%3AX%20support%20for%20select%20Marvel%20Cinematic%20Universe%20and%20concert%20movies.%20Disney%20refers%20