zil%2C%20called%20PineDrama%2C%20dedicated%20to%20micro%20drama%20series.%20Micro%20dramas%20%E2%80%94%20also%20called%20%26quot%3Bverticals%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmini%20dramas%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20are%20serialized%20shows%20that%20users%20watch%20in%20roughly%20one-minute%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20micro%20drama%20series%20often%20include%20romance%20or%20the%20supernatural%2C%20such%20as%20sordid%20love%20affairs%20with%20vampires%20or%20werewolves.%20PineDrama's%20shows%20are%20no%20exception%2C%20with%20one%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BLove%20at%20First%20Bite%2C%26quot%3B%20garnering%2018%20million%20views.%20Its%20current%20top%20three%20trending%20shows%20each%20had%20over%20100%20million%20views%2C%20according%20to%20tallies%20displayed%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20prominent%20micro%20drama%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdramabox-seeks-new-funding-micro-drama-apps-gain-global-momentum-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplatforms%20like%20DramaBox%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ReelShort%2C%20viewers%20can%20usually%C2%A0watch%20some%20episodes%20of%20a%20show%20for%20free%20before%20being%20asked%20to%20pay%20%2420%20a%20week%20or%20more%20to%20watch%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPineDrama's%20business%20model%20is%20unclear.%20Right%20now%2C%20users%20can%20log%20into%20the%20app%20with%20their%20existing%20TikTok%20accounts%20and%20watch%20all%20episodes%20of%20micro%20dramas%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Officer%20Fell%20For%20Me%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Return%20of%20Divorced%20Heiress%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BMy%20Unwanted%20Billionaire%20Ex%26quot%3B%20for%20free.%20There%20are%20also%20no%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221179%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20from%20TikTok's%20new%20micro-drama%20app%2C%20PineDrama.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a8077a645d118818781d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22884%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20titles%20on%20PineDrama%20have%20over%20100%20million%20views%2C%20according%20to%20in-app%20tallies.%3Cp%3EPineDrama.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20interesting%20about%20this%20one%20is%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20they're%20launching%20it%20advertising-free%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20yet%20have%20a%20paywall%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hernan%20Lopez%2C%20founder%20of%20streaming%20consulting%20firm%20Owl%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20He%20said%20PineDrama%20looks%20like%20an%20experiment%20and%20expects%20it%20to%20add%20monetization%20over%20time%20in%20the%20form%20of%20subscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20sign%20that%20vertical%20video%20is%20evolving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20more%20announcements%20this%20year%20from%20many%20other%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicro-dramas-reelshort-dramabox-billion-dollar-business-in-us-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EOwl%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20estimated%20that%20the%20micro%20drama%20format%20had%20generated%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20the%20US%20in%202025%2C%20mostly%20from%20direct%20payments%20from%20viewers.%20Some%20investors%20have%20been%20skeptical%20of%20the%20business%20model%2C%20however%2C%20because%20of%20the%20high%20marketing%20costs%20required%20to%20attract%20new%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPineDrama%20isn't%20TikTok's%20first%20foray%20into%20micro%20dramas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20earlier%20released%20a%20section%20in%20its%20main%20app%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-jumps-into-micro-dramas-buzzy-bite-sized-soaps-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Minis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20viewers%20can%20binge%20on%20bite-sized%20series%20without%20leaving%20the%20platform.%20Many%20of%20the%20same