2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20is%20leaning%20on%20a%20major%20power%20grid%20operator%20to%20bring%20down%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20includes%20calling%20for%20a%20new%20power%20auction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20Trump%20has%20pushed%20for%20tech%20companies%20to%20%26quot%3Bpay%20their%20own%20way%26quot%3B%20on%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20data%20center%20boom%20is%20driving%20up%20electricity%20prices.%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20leaning%20on%20a%20power%20company%20to%20fix%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20a%20group%20of%20governors%20from%20northeastern%20states%20are%20calling%20on%20PJM%20Interconnection%2C%20the%20nation's%20largest%20power%20grid%20operator%2C%20to%20hold%20a%20new%20power%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20allow%20major%20tech%20companies%20to%20foot%20the%20bill%20for%20new%20power%20plants.%20According%20to%20a%20release%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Interior%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoalition%20of%20leading%20technology%20companies%26quot%3B%20has%20committed%20to%20funding%20new%20generation%20capacity%2C%20though%20no%20companies%20are%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20if%20PJM%2C%20this%20faceless%20bureaucratic%20organization%20that%20is%20driving%20prices%20up%20on%20the%20American%20people%2C%20does%20not%20change%2C%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20what%20we%20are%20putting%20forth%20here%20today%2C%20Pennsylvania%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20act%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20go%20at%20it%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20Gov.%20Josh%20Shapiro%20said%20at%20an%20event%20for%20the%20announcement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSiegelScribe%2Fstatus%2F2012211208707768539%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20and%20the%20governors%20are%20also%20urging%20PJM%20to%20make%20a%20series%20of%20other%20changes%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Department%20of%20Energy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Farticles%2Ffact-sheet-trump-administration-outlines-plan-build-big-power-plants-again%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20changes%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EProviding%2015-year%20revenue%20certainty%20for%20new%20power%20plants%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECapping%20the%20amount%20existing%20power%20plants%20can%20charge%20customers%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERequire%20data%20centers%20to%20pay%20for%20new%20power%20plants%20built%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPJM%20operates%20in%2013%20states%20in%20the%20mid-Atlantic%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20Midwest.%20Representatives%20for%20the%20company%20were%20not%20present%20at%20the%20Friday%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20say%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20PJM%20spokesman%20Jeffrey%20Shields%20told%20Bloomberg%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20not%20invited%20to%20the%20event%20they%20are%20apparently%20having%20tomorrow%20and%20we%20will%20not%20be%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Shields%20did%20not%20immediately%20commit%20to%20the%20White%20House's%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPJM%20is%20reviewing%20the%20principles%20set%20forth%20by%20the%20White%20House%20and%20governors.%20The%20PJM%20Board's%20decision%2C%20resulting%20from%20a%20multi-month%20stakeholder%20process%20on%20integrating%20large%20load%20additions%2C%20will%20be%20released%20later%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Shields%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Board%20has%20been%20deliberating%20on%20this%20issue%20since%20the%20end%20of%20that%20stakeholder%20process.%20We%20will%20work%20with%20our%20stakeholders%20to%20assess%20how%20the%20White%20House%20directive%20aligns%20with%20the%20Board's%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAri%20Peskoe%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Electricity%20Law%20Initiative%20at%20the%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20Environmental%20and%20Energy%20Law%20Program%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20administration's%20approach%20will%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20intent%20here%20is%20correct%2C%20which%20is%20to%20appreciate%20that%20data%20centers%20are%20driving%20up%20prices%20in%20PJM%2C%20and%20an%20attempt%20to%20remedy%20that%20for%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Peskoe%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20meant%20to%20isolate%20data%20centers%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market%2C%20and%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20that%20seems%20like%20a%20workable%20approach%3B%20but%20these%20markets%20are%20really%20complicated%2C%20and%20it's%20hard%20to%20predict%20how%20this%20all%20shakes%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20making%20a%20broader%20push%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-microsoft-will-ensure-americans-dont-pay-for-data-centers-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20companies%20to%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20electricity%20consumed%20by%20new%20data%20centers%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20lower%20energy%20costs%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Administration%20is%20working%20with%20major%20American%20Technology%20Companies%20to%20secure%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20American%20People%2C%20and%20we%20will%20have%20much%20to%20announce%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Monday%2C%20adding%20that%20tech%20companies%20must%20%26quot%3Bpay%20their%20own%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20on%20Tuesday%20released%20a%20plan%20that%20includes%20asking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-energy-prices-data-centers-ai-trump-water-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eutility%20companies%20to%20set%20higher%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20f