%20uncrewed%20Black%20Hawk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%20A%20new%20uncrewed%20helicopter%20design%20from%20European%20defense%20and%20aerospace%20company%20Leonardo%20has%20taken%20flight.%20The%20move%20comes%20after%20rival%20US%20defense%20firm%20Sikorsky%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-defense-contractors-future-drone-warfare-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erevealed%20a%20pilotless%20Black%20Hawk%3C%2Fa%3E%20concept%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Royal%20Navy%20on%20Friday%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20UK's%20first%20truly%20autonomous%20full-size%20helicopter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Proteus%2C%20completed%20its%20maiden%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BBritish%20aviation%20history%20has%20been%20made%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20world's%20first%20full-sized%20autonomous%20helicopters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Proteus%2C%20rather%20than%20having%20a%20crew%20in%20the%20cockpit%20or%20cabin%2C%20has%20sensors%20and%20computer%20systems%20%26quot%3Bdriven%20by%20cutting-edge%20software.%26quot%3B%20Those%20allow%20the%20helicopter%20to%20%26quot%3Bunderstand%20and%20process%20its%20environment%2C%20make%20decisions%2C%20and%20act%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Royal%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Royal%20Navy%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20new%20design%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20one-off%20prototype%2Fdemonstrator%2C%26quot%3B%20explaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Navy%20and%20Leonardo%20will%20use%20it%20for%20trials%20and%20experimentation%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20production-line%20machine%20for%20everyday%20usage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20navy%20said%20in%20its%20announcement%20that%20Proteus%20%26quot%3Bwill%20serve%20as%20a%20testbed%20for%20future%20hybrid%20air%20wings.%26quot%3B%20It%20described%20the%20helicopter%20as%20a%20step%20toward%20having%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20operate%20alongside%20crewed%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Royal%20Navy%20operates%20drones%2C%20such%20as%20octocopters%20made%20by%20Malloy%20Aeronautics%20that%20can%20carry%20supplies%20between%20ships%2C%20and%20the%20Peregrine%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bscaled-down%20helicopter%26quot%3B%20that%20does%20surveillance%20missions.%20But%2C%20it%20said%2C%20Proteus%20%26quot%3Beclipses%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20size%2C%20complexity%20and%20above%20all%20autonomy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELockheed%20Martin%20subsidiary%20Sikorsky%2C%20a%20key%20competitor%20in%20the%20helicopter%20space%2C%20unveiled%20the%20autonomous%20U-Hawk%2C%20a%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-skyryse-cooperation-flying-black-hawk-without-pilots-easier-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euncrewed%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dark%20green%20helicopter%20sat%20on%20concrete%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696a630ee1ba468a96aa3512%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221158%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESikorsky%20unveiled%20the%20U-Hawk%2C%20a%20fully%20autonomous%20Black%20Hawk%20helicopter.%3Cp%3ESikorsky%2C%20a%20Lockheed%20Martin%20company%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPentagon%20commitments%20to%20more%20autonomous%20aerial%20weaponry%20have%20pushed%20US%20defense%20companies%2C%20both%20the%20major%20players%20and%20startups%2C%20into%20intensifying%20competition%20to%20build%20these%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20desire%20for%20change%20is%20clear%20in%20the%20helicopter%20space%3A%20US%20Army%20leadership%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20July%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-sec-general-flying-crewed-uncrewed-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvert%20the%20current%20ratio%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20going%20to%2090%25%20drone%20and%2010%25%20crewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEfforts%20to%20develop%20this%20technology%20extend%20beyond%20the%20US%20though%2C%20as%20the%20Proteus%20flight%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220251cf38-0be5-4a3d-a964-9b14d383ae73%5C%22%3EThe%20UK's%20autonomous%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20helicopter%20was%20designed%20and%20built%20by%20Leonardo%20to%20%26quot%3Bunlock%20the%20potential%20of%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Royal%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aim%2C%20it%20said%2C%20is%20to%20operate%20these%20types%20of%20systems%20alongside%20crewed%20aircraft%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%20air%20wing%26quot%3B%20combining%20crewed%20aircraft%2C%20be%20it%20traditional%20rotary%20wing%20aircraft%20or%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20cheaper%20autonomous%20systems%20like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeonardo%20said%20that%20the%20Proteus%20helicopter%20concept%20was%20designed%20with%20a%20large%20modular%20payload%20bay%20that%20can%20carry%20two%20standard%20NATO%20pallet%20loads%20and%20that%20it%20can%20perform%20a%20host%20of%20missions%20ranging%20from%20anti-submarine%20warfare%20to%20airborne%20early%20warning.%20The%20company%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwith%20this%20multi-role%20design%2C%20a%20single%20aircraft%20type%20can%20address%20multiple%20mission%20objectives%20cost-effectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAircraft%20like%20this%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20UK's%20future%20anti-submarine%20warfare%20plans%20under%20Atlantic%20Bastion%2C%20a%20new%20strategy%20aimed%20at%20countering%20Russian%20undersea%20threats.%20Britain%20is%20pushing%20toward%20a%20hybrid%20naval%20force%20designed%20to%20detect%20and%20respond%20to%20submarines%20and%20other%20technologies%20targeting%20critical%20seabed%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20its%20maiden%20flight%2C%20Proteus%20made%20two%20short%20flights%2C%20operating%20from%20the%20Predannack%20airfield%20in%20Cornwall%2C%20in%20the%20southwest%20of%20England%2C%20the%20Royal%20Navy%20s